title: Was the Trump Hotel the capital, Jake Price, on the date of its second fantasy opening?
subtitle: Some followers of QANON conspiracy theories believe that Trump will start a second term on March 4, 2021.
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: The prices of the rooms in Washington, D.C., Donald Trump rose significantly on March 4, 2021 - the date that some of my conspiracy theories believe will be reopened.
